Main Street Inbound

Description:

The Main Street Inbound leaves the University Downtown Center and travels through Main Street in Binghamton & Johnson City and the Pharmacy & Nursing Schools enroute to campus.


Reminder: All Inbound buses at the University Downtown Center return to campus.

Operation Time:

Weekdays:
7:10 A.M. to 9:40 P.M.


Weekends:
10:20 A.M. to 9:35 P.M.

Notes:
